Executes the logs query. Deserializes the result into a strongly typed model class or a primitive type if the query returns a single column.
Example of querying a model:
Response<IReadOnlyList<MyLogEntryModel>> response = await client.QueryWorkspaceAsync<MyLogEntryModel>( workspaceId, "AzureActivity | summarize Count = count() by ResourceGroup | top 10 by Count", new QueryTimeRange(TimeSpan.FromDays(1)));
Example of querying a primitive:
Response<IReadOnlyList<string>> response = await client.QueryWorkspaceAsync<string>( workspaceId, "AzureActivity | summarize Count = count() by ResourceGroup | top 10 by Count | project ResourceGroup", new QueryTimeRange(TimeSpan.FromDays(1)));

